<lb n="0705a02" ed="T"/>他；那由他<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0705001" n="0705001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0705001" n="0705001"/>那由他<anchor xml:id="end0705001"/>為一頻婆羅；頻婆羅頻
